1. DEFINITIONS
================================================================================

"Software" refers to the source code, documentation, assets, and all associated
files distributed under this License.

"NFT" refers to the KPOP CTZen non-fungible tokens issued on the blockchain:
  - V1: https://opensea.io/collection/kpopctzen-official
  - V2: https://opensea.io/collection/kpop-ctzen-v2

"HODDAO Token" refers to the HODDAO governance token available at:
  - https://mint.club/token/base/HODDAO?tab=overview

"Non-Commercial Use" refers to use of the Software for personal, educational,
research, or other purposes that do not directly or indirectly generate revenue
or commercial advantage.

"Commercial Use" refers to any use of the Software intended for or directed
toward commercial advantage, monetary compensation, or revenue generation.
This includes, but is not limited to, operating a commercial service, selling
products derived from the Software, or incorporating the Software into a
commercial product.

"Holder" refers to any individual or entity that owns the required digital
assets (NFTs and/or HODDAO Tokens) as described in Section 4.

