================================================================================
4. COMMERCIAL USE — SPECIAL CONDITIONS (NFT / HODDAO HOLDER REQUIREMENT)
================================================================================

This Software is provided as part of the KPOP CTZen decentralized ecosystem.
Commercial Use of this Software is permitted ONLY to Holders who satisfy at
least ONE of the following conditions:

  CONDITION A — NFT HOLDING:
    The Holder must own a combined total of FIVE (5) or more KPOP CTZen NFTs
    across both the V1 and V2 collections (e.g., 3 V1 + 2 V2 = 5 total).

  CONDITION B — HODDAO TOKEN HOLDING:
    The Holder must own a minimum of FIFTY THOUSAND (50,000) HODDAO Tokens.

CONTINUOUS HOLDING REQUIREMENT:
  The qualifying assets (NFTs or HODDAO Tokens) described above must be
  continuously held in the Holder's blockchain wallet from the date of
  Commercial Use commencement through the date of Commercial Use termination.
  Any transfer, sale, or reduction of holdings below the required threshold
  during this period immediately revokes the Commercial Use license.

PROOF OF OWNERSHIP:
  The Holder bears the burden of proof to demonstrate ownership of the
  qualifying assets. This proof must be verifiable on-chain through the
  Holder's publicly accessible blockchain wallet address. Upon request by
  the Licensor, the Holder must provide:

    (a) The blockchain wallet address(es) containing the qualifying assets.

    (b) Signed message or transaction proof demonstrating control of said
        wallet address(es).

    (c) On-chain records showing continuous holding of the qualifying assets
        for the entire duration of Commercial Use.

