5. TERMINATION
================================================================================

  (a) This License and the rights granted hereunder will terminate
      automatically if the Holder fails to comply with the terms herein.

  (b) Commercial Use rights terminate immediately upon the Holder's failure
      to maintain the required asset holdings as described in Section 4.

  (c) Upon termination, the Holder must cease all Commercial Use of the
      Software within thirty (30) calendar days.

  (d) Non-Commercial Use rights remain unaffected by the termination of
      Commercial Use rights, provided all other terms are met.

